person.persName: William Newton Eulett (Lewis County, Kentucky, farmer.)

body.p: Lewis County, Kentucky, farmer. Kentucky native. Son of John Eulett and Susan Lee Eulett. Resident of Lewis County, Kentucky, in 1850. Farmer in Lewis County in 1860.
